org.gbif.registry.utils

Class Parsers.LegacyDatasetResponseHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.gbif.registry.utils.Parsers.LegacyDatasetResponseHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler
    Enclosing class:
    Parsers

    public static class Parsers.LegacyDatasetResponseHandler
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    Super simple SAX handler that parses all LegacyDatasetResponse elements expected in an XML Response. The resulting string is concatenating all content and inserts a space at every element or attribute start.
    See Also:
    LegacyDatasetResponse
